<br>
One was 61, the other 62. Both of them &quot;complained&quot; about the same thing as you. One day they logged on and deleveled back to 60, went 100% AA and started adventuring in all the &quot;old&quot; zones again.<br>
<br>
They still fight on occasion in tier 1 PoP zones, but mostly they're hanging out in old world places (Kunark and Velious) mixed with a bit of Luclin.<br>
<br>
I'm happy to report that both of them are once more enjoying EQ.<br>
<br>
This might not be the solution for you, but it helped them.<br>
<br>
